        </div>
        <div class="p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-2xl text-center reveal" style="transition-delay: 100ms;">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-4">üöõ</div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-3">Seamless Logistics</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Our fleet manages the entire collection process from your facility to our yards.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-2xl text-center reveal" style="transition-delay: 200ms;">
